divs: Sighting DetailsA few weeks before the picture was taken I had heard that there was supposed to be a semi eclipse happening that day. Around the time that the eclipse was due to happen I had my camera on me so that I could get a picture of this event. I was in the car driving around trying to find the most strategic spot to get a picture but the eclipse never happened. Due to this disappointment I began taking pictures of the sky because the colors just looked bright an fluidlike. After taking a few pictures I went home and uploaded the pictures onto my laptop. after uploading i realized that the pictures that i took of the same part of the sky had a spot that looked as if something was there but wasnt. I can see the shape of some type of ship though when i took the photo all i saw was sky. the photo i uploaded has not been altered in anyways. I do not know what quite to make of the picture that i took but i do believe in a part of me that it is an invisible to the naked eye ship that was coasting through the atmosphere. please contact me if you also see the same ship that i see in the photos because I am very interested in your thoughts on the photo.
Summary: a picture of an invisible aircraft
